cast.original_title: The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds & Snakes
cast.overview: 64 years before he becomes the tyrannical president of Panem, Coriolanus Snow sees a chance for a change in fortunes when he mentors Lucy Gray Baird, the female tribute from District 12.
cast.title: The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds & Snakes

details.biography: Nick Benson was born and raised in Redondo Beach, CA. After doing community theater and school productions, he decided to pursue acting professionally in high school. He was accepted into the BFA Acting program at the University of Southern California and began his career in television and film acting after graduating.
details.name: Nick Benson
